      <title>三星首席执行官大力推广人工智能冰箱和洗衣机，一年后却被遗忘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/samsung-ceo-interview-at-ces-2025-ai-fridges-and-tvs-for-the-smart-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司正在加大对消费电子产品人工智能的投资，押注人工智能在智能手机和电视等设备中的普遍存在将有助于其在人工智能领域占据一席之地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/samsung-ceo-interview-at-ces-2025-ai-fridges-and-tvs-for-the-smart-home</guid>
